  uses  to  itself  one  a  is  a  to  watch .  can Q  The answer must be a situation when a person with mental illness is able to lead a relatively normal life. Managed is a word that describes a situation when a person with mental illness is able to lead a relatively normal life. Effectively treated is a situation when the mental illness is under control. Recur is a word that describes a situation when the mental illness comes back. Cause delusion is a situation when the mental illness is caused by something. Illusion is a word that describes a situation when the mental illness is not real. So the answer is managed (a).

